Products
  -id_shop
  -Title (string)
  -Description (string)
  -Images (json)
  -Combinations (json: size, color, and price)
  -created_at
  -updated_at

Cart
  -id_shop
  -id_customer
  -state
  -created_at
  -updated_at

CartProduct
  -id_cart
  -Product
  -Combination (json: size, color, price, and quantity)
  -created_at
  -updated_at

Customer
  -Wallet Address

Order
  -id_shop
  -id_customer
  -id_cart
  -total_amount

OrderProduct
  -id_order
  -id_product
  -Combination (json: size, color, price, and quantity)

Shop
